examples/JSF_QuickSim/exam05

An example to read a StdHep file ( generator file )
and output new StdHep file after event selection.

OutputStdhepEvents.C defines a class to be used for
event selection.  
Example to use OutputStdhepEvents class will be found in 
UserAnalysis.C.  It is prepared to select large acoplanar 
bhabha events where electron/positron is produced at large angle.

To run the program, do

$  bhabha.sh 

Input file name, output file name, etc are described in 
this script.

5-August-2008  
Akiya Miyamoto

